title: Bigfoot Sightings, North America, 2007
name: Bigfoot Sightings, North America, 2007
description:
Finally, you can determine the best location to spot a sasquatch.

This dataset geo-locates reports of encounters with bigfoot/sasquatch creatures. The reports come primarily from bigfoot resource organization web sites, such as the Texas Bigfoot Research Conservancy (www.texasbigfoot.com).

Data was found online at http://bbs.keyhole.com/ubb/showflat.php/Cat/0/Number/321484/an/0/page/1#321484
